SUMMARY:Pro Jam with Tommy Thomsen
DESCRIPTION:Famous for his guitar and “gravelly” voice\, Tommy Thomsen plays Western Swing – get ready to dance!\nBLUE MONDAYS PROJAM Blues Defenders hosts a weekly concert with headliners and swing dancing. Followed by Pro Jam. An inductee to multiple Western Swing Halls of Fame\, Tommy Thomsen is a music superstar! He plays the classics of Western Swing\, with plenty of entertaining stories along the way from his colorful career. Dance along or sit and toe-tap!\nDoors open at 5pm Show Starts at 6pm. Tickets $15 online. $18 at door. $12 for members.
