DESCRIPTION:It’s Timmy Tracksuit Tuesday!\nTimothy O’Neil Solo Spotlight Show Inside the Big Easy… in a Tracksuit\nTimothy O’Neil hails from Riverside\, California. Currently\, he has found himself rooted in the Folk/Americana Scene of Sonoma County. O’Neil mixes his origin roots of punk rock with a strong nod to bluegrass\, folk\, and a lifetime and adoration for songwriters and songwriting. Be prepared to sing along and have one hell of a good time! \nClub Tuesday – This is a free weekly Tuesday night show featuring local talent
