SUMMARY:John E Crash at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Take a midweek break with great tunes\, delicious food\, and refreshing drinks at Unwind Wednesday — our weekly live music series! \nWhat to Expect: \n• Live music from local and regional artists \n• Special food & drink offerings — enjoy great meal deals and featured beverages \n• Relaxed redwood atmosphere — perfect for unwinding mid-week \nFeatured Artist:\nJohn E Crash \nBay Area & Russian River-area musician known for his energetic and eclectic live performances that blend rock\, punk\, country\, and Americana influences. A 3rd-generation San Franciscan\, Crash has played in a diverse array of bands over the years — from traditional country and Irish-inspired sets to ’80s hair metal and straight-ahead rock/punk — bringing a deeply authentic and wide-ranging musical perspective to every show. \nCrash’s original material spans gritty\, high-energy tracks and thoughtful storytelling\, with releases like “My God\,” “Americaine\,” and “Fixed Gear Johnny” available for streaming. His music often reflects a playful\, irreverent spirit with roots in punk and rock traditions\, making him a memorable presence on local stages throughout the Bay Area and beyond.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/john-e-crash-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.5205;-122.979
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Rio Nido Roadhouse 14540 Canyon 2 Road Rio Nido CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=14540 Canyon 2 Road:geo:-122.979,38.5205
END:VEVENT
