SUMMARY:West Side Stories-Don't Quit Your Day Job
DESCRIPTION:It’s a StorySlam! In fact\, the longest running Slam in Northern California-17 years! We do 5 minute\, True Stories\, Told Live\, On Stage\, Without Notes\, Based on the Months Theme! Come drop your name in the hat to tell or just come and enjoy tales from your neighbors! At the end of the show the entire audience can vote for their favorite. That person receives a $50 dollar cash prize\, their story & picture in The Argus and an invite to our year end GrandSlam on the big stage or The Mystic Theater! What are you waiting for? We’ve been waiting for you for 17 years-come check it out!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/west-side-stories-dont-quit-your-day-job/
