SUMMARY:So Your Friends Think You're Funny #14 - Amateur Comedy Competition!
DESCRIPTION:So Your Friends Think You’re Funny – 14th Edition!\nBarrel Proof Comedy proudly presents the longest-running amateur stand-up competition in Sonoma County\nDate: Wednesday\, 9/10\nDoors: 7 PM | Show: 8 PM\nTickets: $10 advance | $15 door\nLocation: Barrel Proof Lounge \nThink you’re the funniest person in your friend group? Now’s your chance to prove it on stage!\nThe Show:\n8 brand-new comedians perform 5-minute sets.\nJudged live by Casey Williams\, Chelsea Bearce\, & a surprise celebrity guest with real-time feedback.\nHosted by Jon Lehre\nWinner receives $100\, the Pewter Mic Trophy\, and a spot on an upcoming showcase.\nAudience Participation:\nBe part of the judging—you know you do it anyway!\nAudience vote also counts\, awarding the spot\, a trophy\, and bragging rights to the winner (cash excluded).\nPlus\, enjoy a feature set from a surprise headliner!\nWant to Compete?\nLess than 12 months of experience?\nOnly done open mics?\nEmail Booking@BarrelProofLounge.com with “SYFTYF” in the subject line and tell us about yourself.\nOr…just come for the laughs! This is always an entertaining evening full of surprises and fun.\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/so-your-friends-think-youre-funny-14-amateur-comedy-competition/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Comedy
